    "Finally, cyberbullies may also try to isolate their victim by shutting them out of online communities and blocking their efforts to make new connections.",
    "By employing these strategies, cyberbullies can successfully lower their victim's self-esteem and cause them emotional distress.one-shot 1.",
    "Posting negative comments or creating a fake account to post hurtful content about them.",
    "This can range from posting hurtful messages on their social media profiles, to creating an entirely new account and posting malicious content under their name.",
    "This can cause them to lose confidence in themselves, as they may start doubting their own judgement and abilities. 2."
